name: Foxes Of The Opera
description: Foxes of the Opera are the first high-quality 3D-art NFT series launched on the Fantom Opera blockchain. Join 10,000 art-loving foxes at the fox house today and be a part of an endless growing community. Your Foxes will grant you access to the Fox Opera House membership card and give you reign over numerous members-only perks. Check out the www.foxopera.house for more details and follow us at @FoxesOfTheOpera to hear the latest updates.
